# Project Structure

The Virelia app follows a clean architecture with clear separation of concerns:

- Screens are in the `lib/screens/` directory
- Reusable components are in the `lib/components/` directory
- Data models are in the `lib/models/` directory
- Services for business logic are in the `lib/services/` directory

The main entry point is `lib/main.dart`, which initializes the app with the dark mode theme.